creator: John Lord
description:
LibriVox recording of Beacon Lights of History, Vol 2: Jewish Heroes and Prophets by John Lord.

Read in English by KHand.

Volume Two of the series, this book focuses on the leaders of the Jewish faith from Abraham to Saint Paul. Summary by KHand.

For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
